            "title": "Joining Strings 🔗",
            "content": "You can stick strings together using the `+` operator. This is called **Concatenation**.\n\n`'Hello ' + 'World'` becomes `'Hello World'`.",
            "codeSnippet": "let firstName = 'John';\nlet lastName = 'Doe';\nconsole.log(firstName + ' ' + lastName);",
