            "id": "s_l3_4",
            "type": "tip",
            "title": "The Space Trap 🪤",
            "content": "## Don't forget the space!\n\nWhen joining with `+`, JS doesn't add spaces automatically.\n\n`'Hi' + 'There'` = `'HiThere'`\n`'Hi' + ' ' + 'There'` = `'Hi There'`"
